# ACPL Reservation System:

## Group Members:

Aung Aung, Logan Ghast

### Communication Plan:

As of now there are only two members in this project: Logan and I (Aung). This means that our communication doesn’t require anything other than text messages and phone calls. Logan and I will exchange phone numbers, and will discuss our project at least twice a week.

### Project Description:

The goal of our project is to make a system to reserve rooms and computers for the ACPL (Allen County Public Library). 

#### Scope:

The scope of this project might be a bit ambitious (considering our experience), but I believe it’s achievable.   
Main programming language: Python

#### Purpose:

We want to create a GUI that allows the user to reserve a room or a computer and lets the user pick an open time. 

### Responsibilities:

Logan: Front end  
Aung (group leader): Back end  
Both: Middle end
